## Portfolio Project Notice

This is a portfolio/demonstration project created to showcase ML engineering
capabilities. While the code is production-quality, it is primarily intended
for educational and demonstration purposes.

If you use this project as a foundation for production systems, you assume
responsibility for:
- Security hardening
- Scalability requirements
- Compliance with data protection regulations
- Monitoring and maintenance
- API key management and cost controls

